theorem closure_interior_closure_eq_closure_interior_of_P1
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hP1 : Topology.P1 A) :
    closure (interior (closure A)) = closure (interior A) := by
  have hClosEq : closure A = closure (interior A) :=
    Topology.closure_eq_closure_interior_of_P1 hP1
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  ·
    have hSub : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure (interior A) := by
      intro x hx
      have hx' : x ∈ closure A := interior_subset hx
      simpa [hClosEq] using hx'
    exact closure_mono hSub
  ·
    have hSub : interior A ⊆ interior (closure A) := by
      apply interior_mono
      exact subset_closure
    exact closure_mono hSub

theorem closure_eq_closure_interior_closure_of_P3
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hP3 : Topology.P3 A) :
    closure A = closure (interior (closure A)) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  ·
    -- Showing `closure A ⊆ closure (interior (closure A))`.
    have h : (A : Set X) ⊆ interior (closure A) := hP3
    exact closure_mono h
  ·
    -- Showing `closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A`.
    have h : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A := interior_subset
    have h' : closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A := by
      simpa [closure_closure] using closure_mono h
    exact h'

theorem P3_univ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] :
    Topology.P3 (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  simpa using (Topology.P123_univ (X := X)).2.2
